                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-266-victim2250 t18190915-266-viclabel1439"></join>, and had taken the prisoner into my service from the workhouse. I missed this property at different times, and sent for Van, who found the apron concealed in his breeches - he said he had pledged the sheets. I found them at the pawnbroker's.</p>
